{"tid":1330860,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"希望有生之年可以見到全香港connect晒","createTime":"2019-07-18T17:23:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T23:39:39.000Z","uid":37605,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0ea0bb2673e1490008527761c88664b19ded100a","tid":1330860,"uid":37605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:23:17.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我係一名和理非嘅人<br />\n過去喱幾個星期我知道大家都好攰好攰<br />\n議員被dq，遊行又無用，5大訴求又唔聽，衝擊又被人責罵，甚至去到挨打都要話我地嘅年青人係暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我都好明白點解一部分人會開始出現情緒病，有自殺念頭等<br />\n<br />\n即時失意，其實都仲有一班兄弟姐妹互相支持住大家，早排嘅銀髮族遊行更憾動咗我嘅心靈<br />\n所以我地一定要堅持落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知道仲一班持中立意見嘅人甚至撐警嘅人都好，但為咗我地下一代嘅將來，香港人，要we connect呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家7.21企出黎，但唔好再有傷亡啦，每次睇到都好心up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59b1108bb3978f305ad4cb535ea4210db99b9c1f","tid":1330860,"uid":37605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:26:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97e3b3e251c0d2df1429815a1d0d3eb6b9ad5fcd","tid":1330860,"uid":37605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:28:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db343fc41d547124552835d625d11be576179394","tid":1330860,"uid":37605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:31:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2bbae11ba020960c245a2475b573532024aab321","tid":1330860,"uid":37605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T23:39:39.000Z","msg":"push"}]}